text: Jonas Lenherr (born 24 March 1989) is a Swiss freestyle skier. He competed in the 2017 FIS Freestyle World Ski Championships, and in the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male freestyle skiers Category:Olympic freestyle skiers of Switzerland Category:Freestyle skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics
